00:18:19,064 --> 00:18:21,200
- For how long?
- A pretty long time.

306
00:18:21,266 --> 00:18:23,001
- <i>A long time?</i>
- <i>A while?</i>

307
00:18:23,068 --> 00:18:24,903
You know, we'll miss you.

308
00:18:24,970 --> 00:18:26,105
