into a really great memory.

314
00:18:50,295 --> 00:18:53,699
<i>He laughed really hard</i>
<i>at all my silly jokes.</i>

315
00:18:54,900 --> 00:18:58,070
<i>And he very kindly wrapped a blanket</i>
<i>around me when I was cold.</i>

316
00:18:58,737 --> 00:19:01,740
