323
00:20:17,082 --> 00:20:18,550
I was wondering…

324
00:20:19,051 --> 00:20:20,852
It's been a month
since we've been here, right?

325
00:20:20,919 --> 00:20:23,121
- Yeah.
- We even visited Niseko.

326
00:20:24,456 --> 00:20:25,490
I don't know.

327
00:20:25,991 --> 00:20:30,395
