to you in my own way.

328
00:20:30,462 --> 00:20:35,667
- My bad if I didn't come across clearly.
- It did come across.

329
00:20:35,734 --> 00:20:36,868
- It did?
- Yeah.

330
00:20:36,935 --> 00:20:38,437
So, what are your feelings now?

331
00:20:38,937 --> 00:20:42,140
I was wondering
how you're feeling right now.

332
00:20:42,641 --> 00:20:44,977
- Can I be honest?
- Please, go ahead.

333
00:20:47,679 --> 00:20:50,616
Remember the very first time
we went out for a meal?

334
00:20:50,682 --> 00:20:51,717
Mmm.

335
00:20:51,783 --> 00:20:55,754
Since then, my impression of you
gradually changed.

336
00:20:56,255 --> 00:20:58,457
And… looking at you,
I see how cute you are.

337
00:20:58,523 --> 00:21:00,425
- Really?
- But…

338
00:21:00,492 --> 00:21:01,393
Hmm.

339
00:21:02,227 --> 00:21:03,195
Well…

340
00:21:04,296 --> 00:21:08,066
The thing is, I'm not really sure
if I'm interested in you in that way

341
00:21:08,133 --> 00:21:10,402
