347
00:21:22,547 --> 00:21:25,651
<i>I caught a glimpse of your phone</i>
<i>and saw your chat with Hiroya.</i>

348
00:21:25,717 --> 00:21:29,388
<i>I thought, "Oh, there's something</i>
<i>going on between the two of them."</i>

349
00:21:32,224 --> 00:21:35,694
