350
00:21:35,761 --> 00:21:37,329
So, I was wondering…

351
00:21:38,230 --> 00:21:43,135
This is really embarrassing, but I was
thinking, "What if Huwei goes for Hiroya?"

352
00:21:44,403 --> 00:21:46,305
