366
00:22:47,632 --> 00:22:48,967
We still have time.

367
00:22:52,237 --> 00:22:55,006
One more thing. I have this glass bead.

368
00:22:55,073 --> 00:22:56,208
Hmm.

369
00:22:56,274 --> 00:22:58,643
I wanted to give this to you.

370
00:22:58,710 --> 00:23:01,546
- That's so cute.
- You like baby birds, right?

371
00:23:01,613 --> 00:23:03,915
- Wow, it's so cute.
